snippet.title: RetroDoge Dev Update - May 2022
snippet.description:
RetroDoge Monthly Dev Update - May - Castle Demo

New Level - Castle World
- Built in the new tileset
- Animated the lava tiles
- Animated the rotating fireballs + death on touch mechanic

Overall #Gameplay Additions & Fixes 
- Fixed jumping height
- Double jump goes into flip animation
- Ricochet/reflect bullets with #lightsaber  
- Added laser bullets
- Fixed some input keys for movement
- Tested around with timed races

#pixelart #pixelgamerz #pixel
